DSP Default Setting
  • Line Echo Cancellation Tail Length: 2 msec with non-linear linear process
  • Jitter Buffer Control
    • Min. delay: 40 ms
    • Max. delay: 200 ms
    • Optimization factor: 1
  • Voice Active Detection(VAD): Disable
  • Packet loss concealment(PLC): Enable
  • Auto Gain Control:
    • Speaker AGC: Disable
    • Speaker AGC Required Level: Level 1 (up to level 8)
    • Speaker AGC Gain Up: 6 dB
    • Speaker AGC Gain Down: 6 dB
    • MIC AGC: default Disable
    • MIC AGC Required Level: 1 (up to level 8)
    • MIC AGC Gain Up: 6 dB
    • MIC AGC Gain Down: 6 dB
  • Voice Gain:
    • Speaker (Tx): 0dB
    • MIC(Rx): 0dB
  • Caller ID Generation:
    • Software Caller ID generation (Hardware mode is not supported now)
    • Caller ID before 1st Ring as default
    • No Polarity Reversal before Caller ID
    • No Short Ring before Caller ID
    • No Alert Tone before Caller ID
    • DTMF Caller ID:
      • Start digit: A
      • End digit: C
    • FSK Caller ID:
      • Bellcore as default
      • No Date, Time, and Name
  • Caller ID detection: default detect DTMF caller ID only
  • DTMF mode: Inband DTMF
  • Tone of Country: TAIWAN
  • Flash Hook Time: 100 msec ~ 300 msec
